Package: networkGEE
Type: Package
Title: Generalized Estimating Equations for Complex Correlation
        Structures
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Tom", "Chen", email = "tomchen00@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements generalized estimating equations for correlated data
    structures not routinely handled by classical GEE software, including
    independence, simple exchangeable, nested exchangeable, and
    block-exchangeable working correlation models. Supports Gaussian and
    binomial marginal models, deterministic and stochastic fitting routines,
    and robust variance estimation with optional Fay-Graubard adjustment.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.9), RcppArmadillo
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
